title: Kylie Minogue - Boombox (Special Edition) (2009)(cinemiusic.com)
description:
Kylie Minogue releases Boombox, a collection of remixes on January 5th 2009! The album features some of Kylie&#039;s most popular tracks, and some lesser known gems remixed to perfection by some of the best dance producers around including Chemical Brothers, Fischerspooner, Mylo and Sebastien Leger.
